{"tid":2267990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"144名立法會議員及區議員聯署 促懲教署放寬暫停公務探訪安排","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T14:26:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d47140a61228be465343e365735ab62cb423a59b","tid":2267990,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"懲教署自7月中起以抗疫為由暫停所有議員的公務探訪，即使疫情中途曾經放緩，但有關做法一直無放寬。144名立法會及區議會議員今（2日）聯署，投訴署方阻撓申請，令在囚人士的求助個案不斷累積，有違囚友申訴的權利。懲教署回應《蘋果》查詢時，未有提及何時會恢復公務探訪，僅指因疫情反覆，仍維持暫停所有於公務探訪室內進行的非緊急情況的公務探訪，又指會按情況安排在親友探訪室進行有緊急需要公務探訪。<br />\n<br />\n19名民主派立法會議員與近全港三分一區議員，今聯署去信政務司司長張建宗，投訴懲教署由7月20日起至今阻撓議員的公務探訪申請。聯署發起人、議員邵家臻上載信件至社交網站，內容談及署方以「減少進入懲教院所的人流，從而避免疫症流入院所」為由，一直暫停公務探訪申請；惟至疫情緩和時，政府亦多次放寬防疫措施，署方卻無所動作。<br />\n<br />\n信中又指，即使要保障囚友與署方人員健康，同時需要平衡在囚人士有見議員申訴的權利，以及議員有執行職務的公權。聯署要求懲教署跟隨政府放寬防疫措施，盡快恢復公務探訪，並着實訂出放寬疫情放緩客觀標準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/2N26U4CYTBAS3JB2OALG34HXUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F2N26U4CYTBAS3JB2OALG34HXUQ%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=d81099c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F2N26U4CYTBAS3JB2OALG34HXUQ%2F&h=ee63bc44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/2N26U4CYTBAS3JB2OALG34HXUQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ad44c8853f7a6c0fda901dd4efdb6518b533e6d4","tid":2267990,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8ae556645b07165e0fecc6785b7dc72655a6e8","tid":2267990,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"死都唔篤灰<br />\n邊條懲教狗出信話唔比你探咪篤比美國知"},{"pid":"274e32bacc5a45dfb171121715cf7312f626d867","tid":2267990,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"果班懲教狗明攪9手足<br />\n你係制度內投訴呢班賤種,當比你探番<br />\n已經攪9左手足幾個月<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明<br />\nforward封信出去有咩難"},{"pid":"6939d02e8770708ce365769427141afc24141fde","tid":2267990,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbf9e74fac6228d4a44ac0911d4f12c944f879a","tid":2267990,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e48db328ac6ed1a5c4d79f0b8b3dc2669dd9a06","tid":2267990,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb4d2a61166f103a3e4b2e7ad55faa3405b4d2f","tid":2267990,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"早早mark 低 現行 懲教處資料<br />\n<br />\n避免出現好似ss 咁秋後算唔到帳"},{"pid":"4187c1685e5563b72c1a0aa9f5d1f6ab7cef0407","tid":2267990,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2741f8e4ad5e8b50feb4a7fc71d5344664ce04","tid":2267990,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"四百幾位黃區議員得百幾人聯署"},{"pid":"dd873ccc4294f9f7f3fc3143419fe3993d5bbe51","tid":2267990,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i